properties.Name: NY State Bike Route 9
properties.Description: New York State Bicycle Route 9 starts in New York City, follows U.S. Route 9W through the Palisades and connects with Bicycle Route 17 in Wappingers Falls and State Bicycle Route 5 in Albany.   The route continues north to Rouses Point at the the Canadian border -- View in full at http://ridewithgps.com/routes/3593649
